[[Translation:en/Archive/Manual/Settings/Wait twoway signal]]
Sets the wait-time for two-way signals. After this time-out, trains will turn around to see if there is an alternative route. 

If set to 255, trains will wait indefinately.

See also: [[en/Manual/Signals]]

